allEvents.title: Google Cloud and NVIDIA better together for AI/ML Workloads
allEvents.desc: Join us for a live webinar to learn about the powerful combination of Google Cloud and NVIDIA for AI/ML workloads.  We'll cover the following topics:How NVIDIA GPUs accelerate AI/ML workloads on Google CloudThe benefits of using Google Cloud for AI/ML, including scalability, performance, and cost-effectivenessReal-world examples of how organizations are using Google Cloud and NVIDIA to accelerate their AI/ML initiativesThis webinar is ideal for IT decision-makers, data scientists, and engineers who are interested in learning more about how to use Google Cloud and NVIDIA to accelerate their AI/ML projects.

allEvents.title: Google Cloud Startup Summit, APAC
allEvents.desc: Start and scale with AI. Want to scale and grow your startup using AI? Join Google Cloud Startup Summit and hear from top VCs, Google experts, and founders to support your startup journey. Access technical resources, AI insights, and Google Cloud solutions to bridge the gap between inspiration and execution.  At the summit, you'll hear exciting announcements, including how we're expanding the Google for Startups Cloud Program with a dedicated AI program for Seed-Series A startups, which will launch and be open for applications on Apr 25. The new AI startup program will include exclusive benefits such as $250,000 USD in credits for the first year, which is 2.5x the amount we typically offer. To pre-apply for the AI Startup Program, check the box at the end of the registration form.  Guests attending in person will also have the chance to network with investors, executives and experts in the space to expedite their own journey.  Located in JAPAC (Asia-Pacific, Japan)? Visit our JAPAC page to view summit events in your time zone.
allEvents.duration: Hybrid (Online + In-Person Watch Parties)3 hr 5 min
